### Backend development


1. create git repo
    git init
2. Add .gitignore file

3. create .env file for environment variables & read data from .env

4. generate package.json

5. create express app

6. connect to database

7. add middlewares (body parser,err handling middlewares)

8. Design Schemas and create models

9. Design Rest API's for all resources  

### registration & login

10. registration & login in common for user & author. create a separate service to reuse

11. the client 

